        <item>
            <title>【評測】ROBOT 魂高達二號泰坦斯 A.N.I.M.E.　新設計關節超高可動</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/gundammkiianime/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gundammkiianime</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/gundammkiianime/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 12:00:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1235703</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ROBOT 魂的 ver. A.N.I.M.E. 今次啟動了《機動戰士 Z 高達》系列，第一陣作品就是黑色高達二號 GUNDAM Mk-II 泰坦斯。立即來看看錶現如何。</p><p><a title="_DSC9325" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53720486706/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53720486706_3fcff539b2_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9325" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><h2>小美化工作大改善</h2><p>首先，小編一向玩 ROBOT 魂都會加點時間美化一下的，今次的高達 MKII 第一步就是上水貼，在坊間購買 HG 1:144 的高達 MKII Titans 水貼便可，水貼的 Size 都 Fit 好了的；上好所有水貼後下一步就是噴上一層消光處理，完成後就已經極靚仔了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235711" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9253-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9253-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9253.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9259-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9259-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9259.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>開箱</h2><p>我們來看看這次本體高達 MK2 的外殼塗裝及外型，主體高達高約 13cm，外型設計及比例上採用當年的動畫風格設計，裝上所有武裝再擺出角木肇式立姿，甚有風範。整體的分色分件，以及塗裝都細緻，例如背後引擎位置內部也塗上了紅色，製作上頗為用心。不過，外殼的藍色及深藍色則沿用了原始的塑膠顏色，這都是比較膠感的，要下點功夫美化一下才行 (簡單噴層消光便可解決了)。</p><p><a title="_DSC9296" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53720699738/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53720699738_a2e135d9af_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9296" width="939" height="1024" /></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235710" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9251-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9251-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9251.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC9261" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53719585577/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53719585577_21bb7aa17d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9261" width="591" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9270-353x580.jpg" alt="" width="353" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9270-353x580.jpg 353w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9270-scaled.jpg 548w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 353px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235713" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9267-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9267-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9267.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9271-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9271-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9271.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9265-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9265-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9265.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9266-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9266-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9266.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/bandai-g-frame/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Bandai 食玩樂園登陸葵芳     G-FRAME FA 風靈彩透 + MJ GUNDAM SP 版</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/gundam-breaker-4/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《GUNDAM Breaker4》今年登場，特典版情報全公開</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>新設計關節增加可動性</h2><p>現在讓我們來測試一下這個模型的可動性。頭部左右旋轉沒有問題，這次頭部採用了拉出式關節，增加了可動範圍。向前拉出時，嘴部可以碰到胸口；向後也可以抬起頭部。手部可做 360 度旋轉，手肘彎起超過 90 度。兩肩的蝴蝶關節正常向前，還延伸了一個新設計，讓手臂可以拉出，動作的幅度非常誇張，要擺出更有型的動作 Pose 時是非常實用的。腰部的左右旋轉不錯沒有阻礙，向前彎腰約 30 度，亦可向後仰起，雖然幅度不大，但已經能夠做到向上飛的動作，這個設計非常不錯的。腰部左右也可以作輕微活動，高達 MK2 整體的關節鬆緊度也適中。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9273-601x580.jpg" alt="" width="601" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9273-601x580.jpg 601w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9273.jpg 932w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 601px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9275-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9275-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9275.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9276-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9276-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9276.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9277-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9277-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9277.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9278-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9278-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9278.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9279-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9279-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9279.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9280-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9280-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9280.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235726" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9282-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9282-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9282.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9286-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9286-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9286.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>豐富的配件</h2><p>武器及特效件應有盡有，武裝包括伸縮盾牌、鐳射槍、超級火箭炮和掛在頭上的火神炮，鐳射劍；而特效方面則有鐳射直劍、鐳射彎劍、噴射位特效，以及鐳射槍光線特效。而最貼心的是，肩甲，膝甲，及後裙甲，均可替換上印有 1 號及 2 號的裝甲零件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9284-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9284-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9284.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235728" src="h